* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 16-Jun-25 16:00 Page   1
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC1.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC1.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
     2     PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC1.
     3     AUTHOR.        YHAGO.
     4     DATE-WRITTEN.  14/06/25.
     5     DATE-COMPILED.
     6     SECURITY.      SOMENTE O AUTOR PODE MODIFICALO.
     7 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
     8 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
     9     SPECIAL-NAMES.  DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    10 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    11 FILE-CONTROL.
    12     SELECT ARQA ASSIGN TO DISK
    13     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    14     SELECT ARQB ASSIGN TO DISK
    15     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    16     SELECT  ARQC ASSIGN TO DISK
    17     ORGANIZATION IS LINE SEQUENTIAL.
    18 DATA DIVISION.
    19 FILE SECTION.
    20
    21 FD ARQA
    22     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    23     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "ARQA.DAT".
    24 01 REG-A.
    25     02 CODIGO-A    PIC 9(03).
    26     02 NOME-A      PIC X(30).
    27     02 TURMA-A     PIC X(20).
    28 FD ARQB
    29     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    30     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "ARQB.DAT".
    31 01 REG-B.
    32     02 CODIGO-B    PIC 9(03).
    33     02 NOME-B      PIC X(30).
    34     02 TURMA-B     PIC X(20).
    35  FD ARQC
    36     LABEL RECORD STANDARD
    37     VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "ARQC.DAT".
    38 01 REG-C.
    39     02 CODIGO-C    PIC 9(03).
    40     02 NOME-C      PIC X(30).
    41     02 TURMA-C     PIC X(20).
    42 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    43     77 CH-ARQA PIC X(04) VALUE SPACES.
    44     77 CH-ARQB PIC  X(04) VALUE SPACES.
    45
    46 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    47
    48 PGM-04.
    49 PERFORM INICIO.
    50 PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    51     UNTIL CH-ARQA EQUAL CH-ARQB AND
    52     CH-ARQB EQUAL   HIGH-VALUES.
    53 PERFORM FIM.
    54 STOP RUN.
    55 INICIO.
    56     OPEN INPUT ARQA
    57                ARQB
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 16-Jun-25 16:00 Page   2
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
    58          OUTPUT ARQC.
    59     PERFORM LER-ARQA.
    60     PERFORM LER-ARQB.
    61
    62 LER-ARQA.
    63     READ ARQA AT END MOVE HIGH-VALUE TO CH-ARQA.
    64     IF  NOT(CH-ARQA EQUAL HIGH-VALUE)
    65         MOVE CODIGO-A TO CH-ARQA
    66     END-IF.
    67 LER-ARQB.
    68     READ ARQB AT END MOVE HIGH-VALUE TO CH-ARQB.
    69     IF  NOT(CH-ARQB EQUAL HIGH-VALUE)
    70         MOVE CODIGO-B TO CH-ARQB
    71     END-IF.
    72 PRINCIPAL.
    73     IF CH-ARQA EQUAL CH-ARQB
    74         PERFORM IGUAL
    75         PERFORM LER-ARQA
    76         PERFORM LER-ARQB
    77     ELSE IF CH-ARQA LESS CH-ARQB
    78         PERFORM ARQA-MENOR
    79         PERFORM LER-ARQA
    80     ELSE IF CH-ARQB LESS CH-ARQA
    81         PERFORM ARQB-MENOR
    82         PERFORM LER-ARQB
    83     END-IF.
    84
    85 IGUAL.
    86     PERFORM GRAVAR-ARQA.
    87     PERFORM GRAVAR-ARQB.
    88 ARQA-MENOR.
    89     PERFORM GRAVAR-ARQA.
    90 ARQB-MENOR.
    91     PERFORM GRAVAR-ARQB.
    92
    93 GRAVAR-ARQA.
    94     MOVE REG-A TO REG-C.
    95     WRITE REG-C.
    96 GRAVAR-ARQB.
    97     MOVE REG-B TO REG-C.
    98     WRITE REG-C.
    99 FIM.
   100     CLOSE ARQA ARQB ARQC.
